snippet.title: Swift: YouTube - How to Use Enumerations to Prevent Bugs (Ep 10)
snippet.description:
Enumeration is a very powerful concept when building applications that are bug free.  Today, I'll show you how to effectively craft your own enumeration to support our menu component setting names. Hope you enjoy!

How to create a Slide-In Menu Part 1: https://youtu.be/2kwCfFG5fDA

Part 2: 
https://youtu.be/PNmuTTd5zWc

Part 3:
https://youtu.be/DYsfAD01fYk
